This script monitors GitHub issues for trigger comments and automatically
creates pull requests with AI-generated implementations.

Usage:
    issue-monitor [options]

Examples:
    # Run once
    issue-monitor

    # Continuous monitoring
    issue-monitor --continuous --interval 300

    # Process specific issue
    issue-monitor --target-issue 123

For more information:
    issue-monitor --help
"""

